release.changelog: With the new update, we made a small change to the homepage design. Additionally, the new homepage is now more compatible with foldable and tablet devices. We have also added a CPU tab in this update. Through this tab, you can see your CPU's frequency, usage percentage, and temperature in real-time. Moreover, we made some minor design changes to the battery tab and added a shortcut to the device's battery saver settings.
